item.title: About
item.description:
About Me

I am currently an undergraduate student at The University of Michigan studying computer science. I also compete in Capture the Flag cybersecurity competitions with Wolvsec.

About This Site

This site is intented to be a place to share write-ups for CTF challenge solutions as well as updates for my personal projects.

This site is built with static site generator hugo and uses a modified version of hugo-ficurinia as a theme. It is hosted with github pages.
